question: Communication between doctors involved in your treatment helps provide the safest and most effective healthcare. Are you happy for us to inform your GP about this treatment?
Please provide us with the contact details of your GP, in particular their name and fax number (name, house number, street, town, postcode, fax number).
To ensure that you receive your pill quickly, we may want to contact you about your order. Are you happy for us to contact you by phone?
Please enter your phone number (including extension).
